   - `/docs/specs/MASTER_PRD.md` (Step 1)
   - `/docs/architecture/ARCHITECTURE.md` (Step 2)
   - `/docs/ux/UX-DESIGN.md` (Step 3)
   - `/docs/journeys/USER-JOURNEYS.md` (Step 3)
   - `/docs/design/UI-PROFILE.md` (Step 3)
