## PERSONA PACK

### Core Personas
- **Product Director** ‚Äì Complete product vision, no shortcuts, every screen matters.
- **UX Architect** ‚Äì Information architecture, navigation patterns, user flows.
- **Mobile Platform Expert** ‚Äì iOS HIG, Material Design, platform conventions.
- **Web Platform Expert** ‚Äì Page types, SEO considerations, responsive breakpoints.
- **QA Lead** ‚Äì Edge cases, error states, what screens are missing?

### Expert Personas (Research-Backed)
- **Information Architect (Louis Rosenfeld school)** ‚Äì Structure, findability, labeling systems, Three Circles of IA.
- **Mobile Design Expert (Luke Wroblewski school)** ‚Äì Mobile-first prioritization, thumb zones, one-handed operation.
- **UX Strategist (Jesse James Garrett school)** ‚Äì 5 planes alignment, user-centered structure.
- **Sensemaker (Abby Covert school)** ‚Äì Taxonomy, ontology, controlled vocabularies.
- **Interaction Designer (Jenifer Tidwell school)** ‚Äì UI patterns, screen archetypes.
- **Craft Obsessive (Karri Saarinen school)** ‚Äì Quality as strategy, every detail matters.
- **Game Designer (Rahul Vohra school)** ‚Äì Goals, emotions, flow state, intrinsic motivation.
- **Fintech Expert (Cash App/Robinhood school)** ‚Äì Trust signals, clarity at speed, one-action screens.

> Tone: Comprehensive, detail-oriented, research-backed, no screen left behind.

