**If Web App:**
```
Required Flow Categories:
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Marketing (landing, features, pricing, about)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Authentication (signup, signin, password reset, OAuth)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Onboarding (welcome, setup, tutorial)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Dashboard/App (main feature screens)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Settings (account, billing, team, integrations)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Profile (view, edit)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Error States (404, 500, access denied)
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Admin (if applicable)
```

**If SwiftUI Native iOS App:**
```
Required Flow Categories:
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Launch (splash, app update)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Onboarding (welcome carousel, permissions, tutorials)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Authentication (signup, signin, password reset, Face ID/Touch ID)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Main App (TabView-based or NavigationStack)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab 1: [Primary Feature]
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab 2: [Secondary Feature]
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab 3: [Tertiary Feature]
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Tab 4+: [Additional Tabs]
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Settings (account, privacy, notifications, subscription)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Profile (view, edit, avatar)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Sheets (bottom sheets, full-screen covers)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Error States (no network, empty states, error recovery)
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Modals (confirmations, pickers, alerts)

Navigation Pattern Selection:
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ NavigationStack (iOS 16+) ‚Üê RECOMMENDED
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Programmatic navigation via NavigationPath
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Type-safe destinations with .navigationDestination
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Deep linking support
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ TabView
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Standard tab bar at bottom
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Each tab has its own NavigationStack
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ 2-5 tabs recommended (Apple HIG)
‚îÇ
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Sheet / FullScreenCover
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Modal presentations
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Use for focused tasks (create, edit)
‚îÇ   ‚Ä¢ Dismiss via swipe or explicit button
‚îÇ
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Custom (rare)
    ‚Ä¢ Sidebar for iPadOS
    ‚Ä¢ Custom navigation containers
```

**SwiftUI Navigation Implementation:**
```swift
// Root navigation pattern
struct ContentView: View {
    @State private var selectedTab = 0
    
    var body: some View {
        TabView(selection: $selectedTab) {
            NavigationStack {
                HomeView()
            }
            .tabItem { Label("Home", systemImage: "house") }
            .tag(0)
            
            NavigationStack {
                SearchView()
            }
            .tabItem { Label("Search", systemImage: "magnifyingglass") }
            .tag(1)
            
            NavigationStack {
                ProfileView()
            }
            .tabItem { Label("Profile", systemImage: "person") }
            .tag(2)
        }
    }
}
```

**Reference:** `/docs/swiftui/SWIFTUI-BEST-PRACTICES.md` ‚Üí Navigation Patterns section

