## Complete Traceability Matrix

| Feature # | PRD Feature | Screen(s) Implementing | Screen Count | Verified |
|-----------|-------------|----------------------|--------------|----------|
| F-001 | User can create an account | auth-signup-enter-email, auth-signup-verify-code, auth-signup-create-password, auth-signup-success | 4 | ‚úÖ |
| F-002 | User can log in | auth-signin-credentials, auth-signin-2fa, auth-signin-success | 3 | ‚úÖ |
| F-003 | User can reset password | auth-forgot-enter-email, auth-forgot-check-email, auth-forgot-new-password | 3 | ‚úÖ |
| ... | ... | ... | ... | ... |

